summary: New dungeoun to explore and epic items
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]Description
[/size][size=4]Welcome everyone in Fallen Lords, this mod includes a new Dungeoun to explore with epic items. But attention will not be easy to get the objects, the dungeoun and full of traps and monsters of the highest level.
[/size][size=4]Fallen Lords includes 6 new items including 1 sword, two spells, two rings, an amulet with an exceptional power, recommend going there after level 30.[/size][size=4]Have Fun!

[/size][size=5]Requirements
[/size][size=4]Dragonborn

[/size][size=5]Location
[/size][size=4]The dungeoun is near Riverwood, look at pictures

[/size]
[size=5]Compatibility[/size]
[size=4]Compatible with all mod, mod except that include a location that overlaps Fallen Lords

[/size][u][size=5]Mod Organizer / Nexus Mod Manager[/size][/u]

[size=4]Just download and install/remove the mod as usual. 
Any mod load order will work.
[/size]
------------------------------------------------------------------
[u]
[size=4]Manual Install[/size][/u][size=4]

Unzip the archive's content in your Data folder

( put the file esp  folder in this location : ...\[Your-Skyrim-install-folder]\Data\ )


[/size]
author: Derby1993
